<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> June 2026</p>

<p>Just Draft ("the Game", "we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your information.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>Information You Provide</h3>
<p>When using the Game, you may voluntarily provide information through support requests, feedback submissions, or account-related inquiries.</p>

<h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
<ul>
<li>Device type</li>
<li>Operating system version</li>
<li>Application version</li>
<li>Language settings</li>
<li>Anonymous identifiers</li>
<li>Crash reports</li>
<li>Performance diagnostics</li>
</ul>

<h3>Apple Services</h3>
<p>The Game may utilize Apple services including Sign in with Apple, Game Center, StoreKit, App Store purchases, and iCloud services where available.</p>

<h2>In-App Purchases</h2>
<p>All purchases are processed securely through Apple's App Store. We do not collect or store payment information.</p>

<h2>Analytics and Diagnostics</h2>
<p>Anonymous analytics may be collected to improve gameplay, identify bugs, enhance performance, and improve the overall user experience.</p>

<h2>Data Storage</h2>
<p>Game progress may be stored locally on your device and through Apple services when cloud functionality is enabled.</p>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell, rent, or trade personal information. Information may only be shared when legally required or necessary to operate the Game.</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>The Game is not intended for children under the age required by local law to provide consent.</p>

<h2>Security</h2>
<p>Reasonable measures are taken to protect information, though no method of transmission or storage can be guaranteed to be completely secure.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of information where applicable under local law.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<ul>
<li>Apple App Store</li>
<li>Sign in with Apple</li>
<li>Game Center</li>
<li>StoreKit</li>
<li>Apple Analytics</li>
<li>Apple Crash Reporting</li>
</ul>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of the Game constitutes acceptance of any revisions.</p>

